title: Ep 134 | Phil's DIY Mask Secret, Jase's Lowbrow Humor, and the Sleep of Lazarus
description:
Phil takes his semi-annual trip to "the blood man" and discloses his DIY mask technique. Jase teaches Phil the meaning of lowbrow humor with a story that made Missy cringe and explains why John 11 is life-changing. Al shares his medical misery and talks about Karens and when fear turns into anger. And the guys begin a discussion of Lazarus.
